OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early low cloud quickly
OL,6,Fburning away with largely sunny skies
OL,7,Ffollowing. However some higher cloud
OL,8,Fis likely into southern coasts.
OL,9,FStaying rather hot, but breezy for
OL,10,Fmany, and a little cooler across east
OL,11,FKent due to the onshore breeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FWinds easing to become mainly
OL,14,Flight. Some low cloud is possible in
OL,15,Fthe far east, with higher cloud
OL,16,Fcontinuing into southern coasts, but
OL,17,Fotherwise clear skies are likely for
OL,18,Fmost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
