OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FAny early cloud clearing to
OL,6,Fgood sunny spells. Still rather hot in
OL,7,Fplaces, especially in the west, but
OL,8,Fperhaps a touch cooler than recent
OL,9,Fdays with the light northerly breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FFine
OL,12,Fand dry, with plenty of sunny spells
OL,13,Fand likely staying clearer overnight.
OL,14,FCooler than recent days with
OL,15,Ftemperatures easing to nearer normal
OL,16,Ffor mid-July.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
